   (Paris-Diderot University)
   Oral presentation 6.3 : Pre-clinical Imaging: an opportunity to reduce
   and refine in vivo experimentations, A. LE PAPE (CNRS – CIPA)
   o Conclusion:
    The need to improve human relevance in biomedical research , F.
   PISTOLLATO, ECVAM
    Converging technologies and innovative testing platforms , C.E. LIMA
   da CUNHA, EC
